Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}那事也有点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}有点？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}好的 那么就像个男人一样开门见山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}昨晚学校有侵入者 没想到居然是佐藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}不是这样的 我是回来拿教科书的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我就知道是这种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}然后 关于另一个侵入者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}是说那个Cosplay女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}是的 就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}她是我们班里的 和你一样姓佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你知道的吧 有个女生一直没来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊 说起来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}其实啊 关于你们昨晚的非法侵入 我打算不问责了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}但是作为交换 我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}一事相求？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}希望你能成为她——佐藤良子的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我不要 因为我很讨厌那种Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我没有与您做交易的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}这可不是交易 是请求啊 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Men's佐藤和Ladies'佐藤 十分般配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}那么我先失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.82,mark,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}调查书 佐藤一郎 附录
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊 弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊啊 这份文件的内容可绝对不能让学生看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}如果被看到了 我可爱学生的过去就会暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你会接受的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}检测出了龙波动 看来这所建筑物里果然有一个端子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}别胡说八道了 早被戳穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}数秘预测确实观测到了龙端子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}别说这种话了 找一些根本不存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}确认到一郎的品行有显著的劣化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}都怪你吧 我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你才不是什么异世界的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}只是个高中生 随处可见的普通平民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}名叫佐藤良子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}一郎好像受到了波长变换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}出现了呢 专业用语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}觉得随便把很厉害的单词排列在一起就能骗到人就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}波长变换用这边的语言来说就是洗脑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}通过干涉碳素型活动体的脑波…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊啊 够了 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}探寻者只要对一郎的脑波进行再变换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}应该就能解决问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}那要是没能解决的话 你就承认自己是妄想女是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}准备施术了 坐在这张椅子上闭上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}算了吧 根本没有意义 而且我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}若是处理好 你的想法还是没有改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我就承认刚才一郎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你说的啊 承认的话就别再玩那蠢到爆的Cosplay了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我认同一郎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}搞吧 做你那个啥再变换
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}别动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}什…什什什什什
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}看来是再变换造成的暂时的语言混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你就把它看成是施术成功的证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}要搞什么摄影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}能和我们拍照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}诶？不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊啊 喂 别闹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}求你了 求你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}在龙端子探索中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}探寻者是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}而一郎则是奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Slave
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}宣誓完成后 一郎就有听探寻者命令的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}注意人群啊 至少也到没人看到的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}安心吧 探寻者的身姿由于进行了光学隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}Researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}一般人是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}不不 看得见 看得清楚到死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你这设定也太胡来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}别闹啊 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}都叫你别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}求你别闹了 那种地方什么都没有的啦 够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你这身是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}啊 喂 别跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}昨天在车站附近好像有剧组的人在摄影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}佐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}子 子鸠同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}今天来得有点晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}昨天对不起呢 班会结束后等了你五分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}因为你没有回来 所以我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}是 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}所以下次再一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}什 什么时候来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.56,0:24:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}上午七点四十二分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}也就是说比学生们来得都早
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}别扯谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.31,0:24:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}我说你该不是想穿着这身上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.29,0:24:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你终于来学校了呢 佐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}初次见面 我是班主任鸯老
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}鸯老当然只是昵称
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}本来是「鸳鸯夫妇老师」 不知道什么时候被略称成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}佐藤同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}一郎 成年的男性在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.87,0:24:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}在叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.12,0:24:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}探寻者并不叫佐藤
