Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.32,0:33:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}山本 笨蛋 快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.89,0:33:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\3c&H99604B&\4c&HA3715D&}你在干什么
